steps.prompt:
Draft license renewal request letters for media assets that are expiring or have expired.

Asset IDs requiring renewal: {{steps.audit-usage.output.renewal_candidates}}
Violation/warning details: {{steps.audit-usage.output.violation_details}}
Rights system data: {{steps.query-rights-system.output}}
Publication date context: {{publication_date}}

For each rights holder identified in the rights system data, draft a professional renewal request letter that includes: (1) identification of the specific assets and current license terms; (2) the intended continued usage (territory, media type, duration); (3) a request for a renewal quote or confirmation; (4) proposed renewal period of 2 years; (5) urgency note if any asset is already expired or critical.

Format each letter with a clear header identifying the rights holder and asset IDs. Tone: professional and concise.

